These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, mystery, scientific
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, camping, video-games
1. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | scientific | mystery    |
| Hobby     | camping    | video-games       | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, pilot
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, orange, aquamarine
1. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
2. the pilot is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the far left or far right##3
4. the librarian is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | pilot | fisherman | librarian  |
| Color   | blue  | orange  | aquamarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, paramedic, videographer
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, august, september
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
2. the accountant is on the far right##1
3. the paramedic is the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | videographer | paramedic | accountant |
| Birthday   | march        | september    | august        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, canadian
3 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, mouse
1. the canadian is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the canadian is on the left or right of the chinese##3
3. the owner of the fish is between the canadian and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Nationality   | canadian | chinese | brazilian |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | fish    | mouse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
House: victorian, wooden, modern
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, subway, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the victorian house##1
4. the victorian house is between the wooden house and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| House   | wooden | victorian | modern |
| Transport     | subway   | ship   | taxi   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, climbing, ice-hockey
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, engineer, lawyer
1. the lawyer is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | swimming | climbing      |
| Job     | engineer  | lawyer | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold, tulip
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, dutch, malaysian
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the person who growslily##1
3. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Flower   | marigold  | tulip    | lily       |
| Nationality   | dutch | malaysian | australian |

