.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, marigold, lily
1. the person drinking cola is the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk        | fanta  | cola   |
| Flower       | lily | marigold | dahlia |

