2. the fan of disco is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Hobby           | board-games | baking | cooking |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | disco | r&b     |

