.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite
House: tower, colonial, craftsman
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the tower house##1
3. the craftsman house is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the colonial house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
| Beverage   | sprite | milk         | fanta          |
| House        | tower | colonial | craftsman |

