.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, water
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, pumpkin, grapefruit
1. the person eating pomegranate is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking tea##2
2. the person eating pumpkin is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | tea    | water    | sprite  |
| Food   | pumpkin | pomegranate | grapefruit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, colombian, malaysian
There 3 different types of food: carrot, grapefruit, watermelon
1. the person eating carrot is on the far left or far right##3
2. the malaysian is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the person eating watermelon is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating carrot##2
4. the person eating carrot is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | american | malaysian | colombian |
| Food           | grapefruit    | watermelon    | carrot       |

