.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, traveling
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, davidoff, ritmeester
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
3. the ritmeester-smoker is the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | traveling    | baking   | dancing |
| Cigar   | davidoff | ritmeester | oliveros |

