.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
There 3 different types of food: pepper, peas, grapefruit
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, indie, trance
1. the fan of indie is in the middle##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is between the fan of trance and the fan of ambient##2
3. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
4. the fan of trance is the person eating pepper##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Food   | peas | grapefruit | pepper |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | indie  | trance    |

