The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, van
1. the person driving the scooter is the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
4. the havana-smoker is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |    3    |
| Cigar       | alhambra    | havana | baccarat  |
