.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-18::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, rat, rabbit
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the rat is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |       3       |
| Pet       | snake | rat | rabbit |
| Transport   | motorbike  | roller   | snowmobile    |

